    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
        <div class="about-header">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <hr class="divider">
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p>Hello! My name is Will Koeries, and I’m an IT student with a passion for technology and problem-solving. I specialize in web development, coding, and network troubleshooting, with experience in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Python.</p>

                <p>I have a background in web development with a strong focus on frontend and backend technologies. I also provide IT support and work on projects involving data analysis and network troubleshooting.</p>

                <p>My goal is to continuously improve my skills, contribute to innovative projects, and explore the latest advancements in technology. I’m passionate about using my technical abilities to solve real-world problems and eager to take on new challenges.</p>

                <p>When I’m not coding, I enjoy exploring new technologies, learning more about cybersecurity, or helping others solve their IT problems.</p>

                <p>Let’s build something amazing together!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="me.jpg" alt=" Will Koeries's profile photo">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
